lead_paragraph: WEICH--Martin J.,MD., suddenly on April 18, 2016. Esteemed psychiatrist, psychoanalyst, and published author. A man of honor, who spent his life helping people. Beloved husband of Patricia, devoted father of Graig. A real life "Super Hero". He will be forever missed. Service Monday, April 25. Call for details (212) 615-6927. 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  WEICH, MARTIN J.
